title: Tomb of the Demon Priest
story: The tomb of the Demon Priest is situated at the center of a lake. Lately a pack of albino sparrows have made its home here. The tomb of the Demon Priest is a place of growth of a valuable specie of fungi.

notes.text: A large stone gate with a keyhole to the west.
A leather armor and a spear at the bottom of a pool.
A fire in a fireplace, mutes a person when touched.
A stuffed halfling wizard with a crown-shaped key in their hands.
A rear entrance into the tomb.
A corpse of a knight, a holy wand close by.
An artist, sleeping on the ground.
A fresco, totally destroyed by fire.
